library(data.table)
set.seed(22)

tmp <- data.table(x = rnorm(100), y = rnorm(100), z = sample(1:5, 100,
replace = TRUE))

setkeyv(tmp, c("z", "y"))
tmp[, tail(.SD, 1), by=z]

Así puedes sacar los N mayores, etc.

